%%{ init: { 'theme': 'base', 'themeVariables': { 'fontSize': '13px' } } }%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant P as Planner
    participant M as Mutator (Adapter)
    participant QC as QC & Ranker
    participant C as Critic
    participant R as Reporter
    participant SE as StatusEmitter
    participant D as Dashboard

    Note over P,D: === Iteration Start ===

    P->>SE: emit("iteration_start", round_id)
    SE-->>D: iteration_start event

    P->>M: hypothesis + focus_positions + strategy
    Note right of P: Thompson Sampling<br/>selects mutation strategy

    M->>SE: emit("mutation_batch", count)
    SE-->>D: mutation progress

    M->>QC: candidates[] (mutated sequences)

    Note over QC: FlexPepDock parallel scoring<br/>+ ddG calculation

    QC->>SE: emit("docking_progress", completed/total)
    SE-->>D: docking progress bar

    QC->>QC: QC Gate (ddG threshold + structural rules)

    alt Candidates pass QC
        QC->>C: ranked results + pharmacology metrics
        QC->>R: top-K candidates + scores
    else All candidates fail
        QC->>P: no viable candidates (retry signal)
    end

    Note over C: Evaluate diversity,<br/>convergence (Mann-Whitney U),<br/>parameter drift

    C->>P: parameter adjustments for next round
    Note left of C: Adjust mutation rate,<br/>focus positions,<br/>temperature

    C->>SE: emit("critic_feedback", adjustments)
    SE-->>D: critic feedback display

    R->>R: Generate PyMOL renders + Markdown report
    R->>SE: emit("report_ready", report_url)
    SE-->>D: report + visualization update

    Note over P,D: === Iteration End / Loop ===

    alt Converged
        R->>D: Final report + archive summary
    else Not converged
        P->>M: next hypothesis (adjusted parameters)
    end
